PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772121848
OL,3,CBus drivers continue 10-day walkout on
OL,4,Cthe Isle of Man
OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson from
OL,7,Fthe Isle of Man Government said it
OL,8,F'must ensure good value on behalf of
OL,9,Fthe tax paying public, whilst ensuring
OL,10,Ffair salary is on offer to bus
OL,11,Fdrivers.'
OL,13,FDrivers had recently 'received a 3%
OL,14,Fpay increase', adding that 'the
OL,15,Faverage driver earns #36,000 per year'.
OL,17,FThey added that the department 'has
OL,18,Fmade six pay offers to try to settle
OL,19,Fthe dispute'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
