OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772121848
OL,3,CBus drivers continue 10-day walkout on
OL,4,Cthe Isle of Man
OL,6,FThe statement concluded by saying:
OL,7,F'The Department cannot give a running
OL,8,Fcommentary on the negotiations but it
OL,9,Fremains fully committed to engaging
OL,10,Fwith Unite at any time on proposals
OL,11,Fthat could form an acceptable and
OL,12,Faffordable settlement.'
OL,14,FNegotiations are set to continue with
OL,15,Fthe assistance of the Manx Industrial
OL,16,FRelations Service.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
